'''Wisse Dekker''' (26 April 1924 – 25 August 2012) was a [[Netherlands|Dutch]] [[Businessperson|businessman]]. He was the CEO of [[Philips]] from 1982 to 1986. From 1988 until 1992 he was chairman of the [[European Round Table of Industrialists]].<ref>[http://www.ert.eu/about#Milestones%20and%20Chairmen About ERT - Milestones and Chairmen] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150415033652/http://www.ert.eu/about |date=15 April 2015 }}</ref>

